net.sf.jasperreports.engine.export

Class JRXlsExporterParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jasperreports.engine.JRExporterParameter
      • net.sf.jasperreports.engine.export.JRXlsAbstractExporterParameter
        • net.sf.jasperreports.engine.export.JRXlsExporterParameter

  • public class JRXlsExporterParameter
extends JRXlsAbstractExporterParameter
    Contains parameters useful for export in XLS format using apache.poi.hssf APIs.

    The XLS exporter can send data to an output stream or file on disk. The engine looks among the export parameters in order to find the selected output type in this order: OUTPUT_STREAM, OUTPUT_FILE, OUTPUT_FILE_NAME.
